 Popular Nigerian singer, Ayra Starr, has caused a social media buzz after she shared her ordeal at the Lagos passport office. The ‘Rush’ singer lamented over how she was told to remove her lashes. READ ALSO: Ayra Starr Falls On Stage During Performance In Ghana (Video) According to the star, the officials asked her to remove her eye lashes before attending to her. Following the incident, Ayra Starr vowed never to forgive the officers. “This passport office people really made me just remove my lashes. I’ll never forgive y’all.” See post below: 